//! API Upload Tests
//!
//! POST /api/uploads
//!   - Valid JPEG (magic bytes FF D8 FF) -> 201
//!   - Valid PNG (magic bytes 89 50 4E 47) -> 201
//!   - Invalid file type (GIF, PDF, etc.) -> 400, "Magic bytes do not match"
//!   - File > 10MB -> 400, "exceeds maximum size"
//!   - Duplicate fingerprint -> 409, "Duplicate file"
//!   - CSRF required -> 403
//!   - MerchantStaff+ required -> 403 for Customer
EOF

cat > /Users/mac/TASK-w2t76/repo/API_tests/test_api_audit.rs << 'EOF'
//! API Audit Tests
//!
//! GET /api/audit
//!   - PlatformOps+ required -> 403 for Customer/MerchantStaff
//!   - Returns recent audit entries
//!   - Filters by resource_type and resource_id
//!
//! Audit chain verification:
//!   - Each entry's previous_hash matches the prior entry's current_hash
//!   - Recomputed hash matches stored current_hash
//!   - Tampered entry breaks chain validation
//!
//! Actions that create audit entries:
//!   - LOGIN, LOGOUT
//!   - CREATE/UPDATE/DELETE on all resources
//!   - STATUS_CHANGE on vehicles
//!   - REDEEM, UNDO on tickets
//!   - EXPORT
//!   - BACKUP, RESTORE
//!   - PERMISSION_CHANGE
EOF
